name: ComplimentMe
0:
”Alexa, open get a compliment”
”Alexa, launch get a compliment”
”Give me a compliment”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: get a compliment
des: The ComplimentMe skill gives a random compliment to the user upon request. If you say 'Compliment me' or 'Give me a compliment', you will get a sweet or funny compliment in response to brighten up your day, make you laugh, or to entertain guests.
